snippet.title: NORDIC ASHES: Survivors of Ragnarok - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2068280/Nordic_Ashes_Survivors_of_Ragnarok
itchio: https://noxfall-studios.itch.io/nordic-ashes
Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/nordic-ashes/737195
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/RhdgScwtm9

A Norse themed rogue-lite enemy hell, where you’ll have to survive hordes of creatures that come your way. Unlock new weapons and abilities as you battle. Upgrade your character’s stats with constellation ability trees and slay your enemies before they surround you, or it may be too late…
